                    &nbsp;and&nbsp;
                    <span class="courses"> C++ Courses </span>
                    will be out soon!
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-8">
                    <h1 class="heading">
                            LEARN.EXPLORE.<br>CODE.
                    </h1>
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    <h4 class="next-heading">Sharp your Coding Skills with Us!</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-4">
                <div class="row ">
                    <img src="images/computer.png" style="width:100%;height:100%;">
                </div>
            </div>  
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
                   <a href="/problems"><button class="btn btn-primary">Explore Problems</button></a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-6">
